node.text: 8 years… still can’t talk about it. 💔 You are my light, I know it’s you guiding me. We love and miss you so much. The things I would do for just 10 more seconds with you. Forever in my heart and always on my mind! Can’t nothing in this world fix my broken heart when it comes to you. Come see me in my dreams tonight, it’s been a while. Forever KYLE!
